name: THE GOONEEZ - RAD! ft. Andy Milonakis

metadata.description:
The year was 2015 - We were on tour doing a show in Laughlin, Nevada and on the bill with us was a guy who's show i grew up watching on MTV... pop culture icon & comedian, Andy Milonakis. 

I used to hear him freestyle on 'The Andy Milonakis Show' and always thought he had mad skills with funny wordplay. Well the night of the show i watched his set and realized he was a serious emcee with a passion for hip-hop music, crazy stage presence and ill comedic gift between bars. 

We ended up connecting on new song called 'RAD!' dropping exclusively for soundxyz. Add this to your collection & premint the drop.
metadata.name: RAD! ft. Andy Milonakis #1
metadata.title: RAD! ft. Andy Milonakis
